Class RegistrationDTO

java.lang.Object
common.dto.RegistrationDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RegistrationDTO extends Object implements Serializable
DTO used for subscriber registration.

Carries all required data to create a new subscriber account, including credentials, personal details and identification data.

      username - login username

      fullName - subscriber full name

      email - email address
      memberCode - unique member code
      barcode - encoded barcode/QR identifier
